    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Vendetta closes distance with Soaring Slice and Whirlwind Dash to engage in melee range, using Warding Stance to block incoming damage and Onslaught&#39;s speed bonus to chain kills together.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Warding Stance only blocks frontal damage and drains her energy, so flanking her or catching her from behind while she&#39;s engaged with another target removes her only defensive tool.</p>\n"
